snippet.title: Deadly Rain - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Deadly Rain is a survival horror FPS game that puts you in a terrifying fight for survival against hordes of scary mutants in a rainy, abandoned village. Find and manage resources to stay alive in the worst and most unexpected situations.
💎 BUY NOW: https://shortly.at/J8NBf
